{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01UsiGacZr6ere33HyN2o8mT","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The task is to update documentation to reflect the current source code. Let me check what's already implemented vs what the docs say.\n\nLooking at the source code:\n1. `Wire` struct has `OutputMap []OutputMapping` - done\n2. `OutputMapping` has `EnvVar` and `Path OutputPath` - done\n3. `OutputPath.Evaluate()` method - done\n4. Duplicate output mapping validation in `Workflow.Validate()` - done (lines 214-226)\n5. Tests for duplicate output mapping validation - done (4 tests at lines 339-447)\n\nThe design doc already describes all of this accurately. \n\nNow I'm checking the workflows.md documentation to see if there are any gaps or outdated sections that need updating.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13834,"cache_read_input_tokens":15258,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":13834},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b5cb00e3-b191-4d07-96b7-3f5680038ecb","uuid":"64f0d87a-a32a-43cb-89de-2580242b57e3"}
